---
title: Chard & Wild Mushroom Penne
description: Garlicky wild mushrooms and swiss chard are front and center in this creamy pasta. We've spiced it up with a sprinkle of paprika and a dash of chili flakes. Parmesan cheese does the trick to make this penne a real winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d3cfce6ced6e7b368b456a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54d3cfce6ced6e7b368b456a.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 611 kcal
  fat: 23 g
  carbohydrates: 81 g
  protein: 25 g
  fiber: 12 g
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Italian
author: HelloFresh
